<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>ṭwbạk yạ mskyn</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- ṭwbạk yạ mskyn fhạ lk ạlsmạʾ
 ṭwbạk yạ ḥzyn yḥlw lk ạlʿzạʾ
 ạlqrạr- ṭwbạk ṭwbạk fhạ lk ạlsmạʾ
 ṭwbạk yḥlw lk ạlʿzạʾ
 2- llwdʿạʾ ṭwby̱ fạlạ̉rḍ yrtẖwn
 wạlrḥmạʾ ạ̹dẖ hm kdẖạk yrḥmwn
 lạ̉nqyạʾ ạlqlb fạllh ybṣrwn
 lṣạnʿy ạlslạm ạ̉bnạʾh ydʿwn</lyrics>
